PRIMARY ARTICLE:
Title: {{ $json.title }}
Source: {{ $json.source }}
URL: {{ $json.link }}
Snippet: {{ $json.description }}

EXTERNAL SEARCH REFERENCES FOR CROSS-VERIFICATION:
{{ $json.searchResultsText }}

CREATOR NICHE CONTEXT:
{{ $json.niche }}

CREDIBILITY RULES TO APPLY:
{{ $json.credibilityRules }}

Evaluate and return a single JSON object. Ensure it contains EXACTLY these fields:
{
  "credibilityScore": <integer 1 to 10>,
  "credibilityExplanation": "<2 sentence analysis of whether the references confirm or refute the primary news>",
  "summary": "<punchy 3 sentence summary of the news tailored to the niche>",
  "isBreaking": <boolean indicating if this is highly urgent, novel or massive breaking news>,
  "suggestedTweet": "<an engaging tweet/thread-starter for X (under 280 chars) with hooks and hashtags, referencing the news>"
}

